<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Television">Television</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Peter_Lovesey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Television">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
<p>The television series <i><a href="/wiki/Cribb" title="Cribb">Cribb</a></i> (1980–81) is available on DVD in the UK, the US, and Canada.</p>
